    "license": "Apache-2.0",
    "notes": "Explicit counter/gauge classification for SHOW GLOBAL STATUS variables that the exporter classifies as Untyped (i.e. variables not matched by globalStatusRE). Variables covered by the regex (Com_*, Handler_*, Connection_errors_*, Innodb_rows_*, Performance_schema_*, Innodb_buffer_pool_pages_*) are classified by code and need not appear here unless they require an override (e.g. Innodb_buffer_pool_pages_total, which the exporter skips but we still want to show as a gauge)."
  },

